    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that still looks and feels great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a quality car that's ready to go, this is the one! Feel free to shout if you have any questions!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
