    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior maintains a brilliant gloss, with only the slightest stone chips on the front fascia that testify to its time on the road. Inside, you\u2019ll find a meticulously kept cabin; the upholstery is free of cracks or stains, and the dashboard remains pristine with all electronic features and climate controls operating flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust, having undergone regular servicing with a full history available for review. It shifts smoothly, brakes confidently, and sits on a set of tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a turn-key vehicle, perfectly suited for someone who wants a reliable, high-quality driving experience without the premium price tag of a brand-new model.",
      "price": 36500.0,
