      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been so reliable and is still in wonderful shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. It\u2019s been well-loved, kept clean, and honestly runs like a dream. You\u2019re going to love how it handles on the road! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
